com.here.android.mpa.venues3d

Interface VenueService.VenueServiceStopListener

  • Enclosing class:
    VenueService

    public static interface VenueService.VenueServiceStopListener
    Represents a listener to provide notification of the venue service's status upon its stopping.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onVenueServiceStopped()
      This callback is called after Venue loading has been stopped using VenueService.stopAsync(VenueService.VenueServiceStopListener) and no more venues are being loaded any more.
